==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unguiculated
<hw>Un*guic"u*la`ted</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>,
}</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Furnished with nails, claws, or
hooks; clawed. See the Note under <er>Nail</er>, <pos>n.</pos>,
1.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Furnished with a claw, or a narrow
stalklike base, as the petals of a carnation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unguiferous</ent>⟦br⟧
